# Include repo-committed agent skills in the sdist. The files live outside
# src/codeprobe/ so they cannot be declared in [tool.setuptools.package-data];
# this MANIFEST.in + `include-package-data = true` in pyproject.toml is the
# equivalent mechanism for setuptools builds. See PRD §7 (paired-skills).
recursive-include .claude/skills SKILL.md
